item.description: This 10 week class is geared to assist you in becoming aware of where you are in becoming aware of where you are on your path, why you are there and how to get to where you want to be. Combining science and spirituality, pragmatic and alternative knowledge, this class will provide you with tools that you can utilize to create an amazing and purposeful life. A three tiered approach to psychic awareness, this class provides you with valuable tools that allow you to open up intuitively, hone your psychic abilities and begin living in abundance and spiritual flow. If you find yourself presented with difficulties, are wishing to open up intuitively and psychically or if you are simply ready to make a change in your life, this class will provide you with tools to do just that!
item.name: Spiritual Awakening/Psychic Development Class
